{"tid":120963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(中華民族)教師斥中史科修訂﹕頌大一統少談亂亡","createTime":"2017-02-15T00:16:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T04:22:00.000Z","uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a621f76b3d25a168aff6a5dbd3308375cd46aec","tid":120963,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T00:16:51.000Z","msg":"&lt;回帶&gt;<br />\n教師斥中史科修訂﹕頌大一統少談亂亡<br />\n有教師質疑新課程強調歷朝盛世、民族融和部分，減省國家衰亡、起義部分，是歌頌大一統與融和；亦有教師質疑，香港史部分非以港人為中心，而是將香港史變成中國歷史的附庸。<br />\n<a href=\"http://life.mingpao.com/htm/hkdse/cfm/news3.cfm?File=20160930/news/gfa1.txt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flife.mingpao.com%2Fhtm%2Fhkdse%2Fcfm%2Fnews3.cfm%3FFile%3D20160930%2Fnews%2Fgfa1.txt&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=2f3916bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Flife.mingpao.com%2Fhtm%2Fhkdse%2Fcfm%2Fnews3.cfm%3FFile%3D20160930%2Fnews%2Fgfa1.txt&h=743d5476\" target=\"_blank\">http://life.mingpao.com/htm/hkdse/cfm/news3.cfm?File=20160930/news/gfa1.txt</a>"},{"pid":"dc3e401da76a5786a4c86caf768fb73a8ce5c566","tid":120963,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:35:20.000Z","msg":"中華民族=56個不種族炒埋一大碟"},{"pid":"16f8abbcaa40c617e8e83908a1b29ca90c41b6d7","tid":120963,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:41:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中華民族=56個不種族炒埋一大碟</blockquote><br />\n連咩叫漢人都冇清楚定義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a53080118dd28359dd40a463dac4e8a0512ab95f","tid":120963,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T04:06:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中華民族=56個不種族炒埋一大碟</blockquote><br />\n連咩叫漢人都冇清楚定義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n南北朝<br />\n魏晉以來的民族融合<br />\n<br />\n魏晉南北朝時期出現的民族大遷徙、大融和，使中華民族的內涵更為豐富，也為日後的隋唐盛世奠定了堅實的基礎。看到這裡，相信不少朋友會自問：「我有沒有匈奴、鮮卑或其他胡人的血統呢？」也有人會說：「怎麼我的祖先起源於北方？」<span style=\"color: red;\">原來今日之漢族早已是個大雜燴。</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.china10k.com/trad/history/3/33/33d/33d01/33d0101.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.china10k.com%2Ftrad%2Fhistory%2F3%2F33%2F33d%2F33d01%2F33d0101.htm&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=2b591e96\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.china10k.com/trad/history/3/33/33d/33d01/33d0101.htm</a>"},{"pid":"30b87a1eb6aee80d66063ea0b57d4dc6121b00a3","tid":120963,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T04:08:53.000Z","msg":"所以支那人成日憑咩叫日本人尊重歷史<br />\n收撚皮啦"},{"pid":"eb05d50ae10ddfc3a384b455a2a5683f4de2f52b","tid":120963,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T04:16:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中華民族=56個不種族炒埋一大碟</blockquote><br />\n連咩叫漢人都冇清楚定義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n南北朝<br />\n魏晉以來的民族融合<br />\n<br />\n魏晉南北朝時期出現的民族大遷徙、大融和，使中華民族的內涵更為豐富，也為日後的隋唐盛世奠定了堅實的基礎。看到這裡，相信不少朋友會自問：「我有沒有匈奴、鮮卑或其他胡人的血統呢？」也有人會說：「怎麼我的祖先起源於北方？」<span style=\"color: red;\">原來今日之漢族早已是個大雜燴。</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.china10k.com/trad/history/3/33/33d/33d01/33d0101.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.china10k.com%2Ftrad%2Fhistory%2F3%2F33%2F33d%2F33d01%2F33d0101.htm&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=2b591e96\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.china10k.com/trad/history/3/33/33d/33d01/33d0101.htm</a></blockquote><br />\n魏晉南北朝400年間<br />\n劉邦氏族被殺光<br />\n中原所謂華夏民族 <br />\n大量被殺 向四方逃走<br />\n中原變成胡人天下 <br />\n跟漢人通婚雜居<br />\n何有漢族？"},{"pid":"61fdeece99a1922904eeb59b7fa4df514a4591c0","tid":120963,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T04:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中華民族=56個不種族炒埋一大碟</blockquote><br />\n連咩叫漢人都冇清楚定義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n南北朝<br />\n魏晉以來的民族融合<br />\n<br />\n魏晉南北朝時期出現的民族大遷徙、大融和，使中華民族的內涵更為豐富，也為日後的隋唐盛世奠定了堅實的基礎。看到這裡，相信不少朋友會自問：「我有沒有匈奴、鮮卑或其他胡人的血統呢？」也有人會說：「怎麼我的祖先起源於北方？」<span style=\"color: red;\">原來今日之漢族早已是個大雜燴。</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.china10k.com/trad/history/3/33/33d/33d01/33d0101.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.china10k.com%2Ftrad%2Fhistory%2F3%2F33%2F33d%2F33d01%2F33d0101.htm&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=2b591e96\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.china10k.com/trad/history/3/33/33d/33d01/33d0101.htm</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1947e175a70aca88d618ad9b7df4e015bcf3e8d5","tid":120963,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T04:22:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中華民族=56個不種族炒埋一大碟</blockquote><br />\n連咩叫漢人都冇清楚定義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n南北朝<br />\n魏晉以來的民族融合<br />\n<br />\n魏晉南北朝時期出現的民族大遷徙、大融和，使中華民族的內涵更為豐富，也為日後的隋唐盛世奠定了堅實的基礎。看到這裡，相信不少朋友會自問：「我有沒有匈奴、鮮卑或其他胡人的血統呢？」也有人會說：「怎麼我的祖先起源於北方？」<span style=\"color: red;\">原來今日之漢族早已是個大雜燴。</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.china10k.com/trad/history/3/33/33d/33d01/33d0101.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.china10k.com%2Ftrad%2Fhistory%2F3%2F33%2F33d%2F33d01%2F33d0101.htm&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=2b591e96\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.china10k.com/trad/history/3/33/33d/33d01/33d0101.htm</a></blockquote><br />\n魏晉南北朝400年間<br />\n劉邦氏族被殺光<br />\n中原所謂華夏民族 <br />\n大量被殺 向四方逃走<br />\n中原變成胡人天下 <br />\n跟漢人通婚雜居<br />\n何有漢族？</blockquote><br />\n走到來南方定居中原人<br />\n有些跟南方種族通婚<br />\n就話南方人係南方漢人<br />\n又變成佢地領土 完善中華民族版圖"}]}